<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Page</title>
    <%= stylesheet_link_tag 'about' %>
</head>

<body>
    <header>
        <h1>National Wildlife Parks</h1>
        <h2>My rails Application</h2>
    </header>
    <main>
        <section>
            <h2>Data Sources</h2>
            <p>My rails application uses the following data sources:</p>
            <ol>
                <li>Parks: 100 randomly generated parks with details such as name, location, established date, size, and description.</li>
                <li>Visitors: 200 randomly generated visitors with details such as park ID, year, total visitors, and camping visitors.</li>
                <li>Wildlife: 200 randomly generated wildlife records with details such as park ID, species name, habitat, and population status.</li>
                <li>Facilities: Randomly generated facilities such as visitor centers, picnic areas, playgrounds, and trails.</li>
            </ol>
        </section>
        <section>
            <h2>Entity Relationship Diagram (ERD)</h2>
            <p>My Rails application ERD represents the relationships between the Park, Visitor, Wildlife, and Facility entities.</p>
            <img src="<%= image_path('erd.jpg') %>" alt="ERD">


        </section>
    </main>
    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 My Rails Application. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>